'''Nash Edgerton''' (born [[January 19]], [[1973]]) was, during the filming of the [[prequel trilogy]], a stunt double for [[Ewan McGregor]] ([[Obi-Wan Kenobi]]).

==Biography==
Edgerton is the brother of [[Joel Edgerton]] ([[Owen Lars]]). By coincidence, Obi-Wan and Owen were referred to as brothers in the [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Return of the Jedi'']] [[Star Wars: Return of the Jedi (novelization)|novelization]].

Nash has also directed numerous short films and television episodes, as well as two feature-length films, ''The Square'' (2008, co-starring and co-written by Joel), and the action/comedy ''Gringo'', starring Joel and [[David Oyelowo]].

